\tan 15^\circ &= \frac{1 - \frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}}{1 + \frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}} \cdot \frac{1 - \frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}}{1 - \frac{\sqrt{3}}{3}} \\
